          "title": "Daily AI News Digest Guide",
          "entityId": "daily-news-guide",
          "metadata": {
            "sizeMode": "compact",
            "status": "ready",
            "version": 0
          },
          "contentPreview": "## Daily AI News Digest Workflow\n\n### 🎯 Pre-configured Setup\n**Smart Defaults Included:**\n- ⏰ Schedule: Daily at 9:00 AM\n- 🔍 Topics: AI research, ML, LLM, robotics, computer vision\n- 📧 Format: Professional newsletter style\n- 📊 Sources: Top 12 quality sources from reliable publishers\n\n### 🚀 How It Works\n1. **Schedule Daily Trigger** - Auto-runs at your configured time (@schedule_time)\n2. **Perplexity AI News Fetcher** - Searches for latest AI news using your topics and categories\n3. **Content Extraction** - Pulls detailed content with preserved citations\n4. **Digest Formatting** - Applies your selected format style (@digest_format)\n5. **Gmail Draft** - Creates professional HTML email for @recipient_email\n6. **Manual Approval** - Review and approve before sending\n7. **Delivery** - Send to your Gmail inbox with tracking\n\n### ⚙️ Required Configuration\n- 📧 **Gmail recipient address** (required)\n- 🔑 **Perplexity API key** (required)\n\n### 🎨 Customization Options\n- **Search Topics**: Customize what AI news to fetch\n- **Categories Focus**: Fine-tune content filtering\n- **Schedule Time**: Change from default 9:00 AM\n- **Format Style**: Professional, Concise, or Detailed\n\n### 💡 Pro Tips\n- Ensure Perplexity API key has news access permissions\n- Gmail API requires send permissions for delivery\n- Always review the approval step before final send\n- Monitor delivery confirmations for reliability\n",
          "memoType": "workflow_documentation",
          "updatedAt": "2025-10-13T08:00:00.722Z"
        }
